# type: textblock
#: ../../doc/po4a.7.pod:1151
msgid ""
"One of my dreams would be to integrate somehow po4a to gtranslator or "
"kbabel. When a sgml file is opened, the strings are automatically "
"extracted.  When it's saved a translated sgml file can be written to disk. "
"If we manage to do a MS Word (TM) module (or at least RTF) professional "
"translators may even use it."
